
===================================
📌 1. Finglish Version (Persian Latin Script)
===================================

📖 **Tashrih:**
    Dastoor `hp-doctor` yek abzar baraye diagnos va halle moshkelat dar dastgah-ha-ye HP (printer-ha, scanner-ha, va digar dastgah-ha) ast. In abzar be shoma komak mikonad ta moshkelat ra peyda konid va rah hal-ha-ye pishnahadi ra estefade konid.

⚙️ **Gozine-ha:**
    🔹 `hp-doctor` --> 🩺 Shoru' kardane abzar ba GUI (graphical user interface).
    🔹 `hp-doctor scan` --> 🔍 Scan kardane dastgah baraye moshkelat.
    🔹 `hp-doctor troubleshoot` --> 🛠️ Dastoor halle moshkelat ra ejra mikonad.
    🔹 `hp-doctor update` --> ⬆️ Update kardane hp-doctor be akharin version.

🛠 **Mesal-ha:**

    $ hp-doctor

    🔹 Run kardane abzar ba GUI baraye diagnos va halle moshkelat.

    $ hp-doctor scan

    🔹 Scan kardane dastgah-ha-ye motasel baraye moshkelat.

✅ **Mesal sade:**

    $ hp-doctor troubleshoot printer

    🔹 Hal kardane moshkelat printer be soorat khodkar ba estefade az pishnahadat hp-doctor.

===================================
📌 2. English Version
===================================

📖 **Description:**
    The `hp-doctor` command is a tool for diagnosing and troubleshooting issues with HP devices (printers, scanners, etc.). It helps you identify problems and apply suggested solutions.

⚙️ **Options:**
    🔹 `hp-doctor` --> 🩺 Starts the tool with a GUI (graphical user interface).
    🔹 `hp-doctor scan` --> 🔍 Scans the device for problems.
    🔹 `hp-doctor troubleshoot` --> 🛠️ Runs the troubleshooting routine.
    🔹 `hp-doctor update` --> ⬆️ Updates hp-doctor to the latest version.

🛠 **Examples:**

    $ hp-doctor

    🔹 Runs the tool with a GUI to diagnose and troubleshoot issues.

    $ hp-doctor scan

    🔹 Scans connected devices for problems.

✅ **Simple Example:**

    $ hp-doctor troubleshoot printer

    🔹 Automatically troubleshoot printer problems using hp-doctor's suggestions.
